00:05:05.618 --> 00:05:07.859
Kamu merasa bersalah
karena meninggalkan temanmu?

00:05:43.100 --> 00:05:46.553
-Oh, Tuhan, enggak!
-Dia enggak tahan dipukul!

00:05:53.977 --> 00:05:57.115
Tolong, jangan pukul dia.
Oh, Tuhan, jangan!

00:05:57.248 --> 00:05:59.193
Oh, Tuhan!

00:06:02.812 --> 00:06:05.731
Tolong ampuni dia, Ayya!

00:06:12.459 --> 00:06:15.290
Aku bingung harus gimana!

00:06:19.044 --> 00:06:21.786
Ayya, aku bingung harus melakukan apa.

00:06:22.279 --> 00:06:28.876
Oh, enggak, mereka memukulmu
sampai mati tanpa ampun.

00:08:18.330 --> 00:08:19.096
Buruan!

